[[2008年夏季残奥会|2008年夏季残奥会]]是历史上举行的第13届夏季残奥会，该运动会每四年举办一届，专门为世界各国身患[[残疾|残疾]]的[[运动员|运动员]]提供同场竞技的舞台。本届残奥会于2008年9月6日至17日在[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]][[首都|首都]][[北京|北京]]举办<ref name="general information">{{Cite web |title=Beijing 2008 |url=http://www.paralympic.org/paralympic-games/beijing-2008 |accessdate=2013-07-23 |publisher=Paralympic.org |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507095929/http://paralympic.org/paralympic-games/beijing-2008 |archivedate=2013-05-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

本届残奥会共有来自146个国家和地区的3951名运动员参加了20个类别的472项比赛角逐，其中[[布隆迪|布隆迪]]、[[加蓬|加蓬]]、[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]、[[海地|海地]]和[[黑山|黑山]]都是首次参加残奥会。无论是在参与国家数量上，还是运动员的总数上都创下了新的纪录<ref name="general information" />。奖牌的设计与[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]所颁发的基本相同<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/graphic/n214342419.shtml |title=Design Concept for the Medals of the Beijing 2008 Paralympic Games |newspaper=Beijing 2008 Paralympic Games |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825073417/http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/graphic/n214342419.shtml |archivedate=2012-08-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，将[[玉|玉]]制碟片嵌入金属奖牌中，三种奖牌所使用玉的颜色各不相同。来自[[中央美术学院|中央美术学院]]、[[清华大学|清华大学]]和[[中国印钞造币总公司|中国印钞造币总公司]]的设计师一共提交了21种不同的设计方案，最终获选者在2007年夏确定<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://en.beijing2008.cn/paralympic/news/news/n214196157.shtml |title=Medals unveiled for Paralympic Games of 2008 |date=2007-11-14 |newspaper=''Beijing 2008'' |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110221120204/http://en.beijing2008.cn/paralympic/news/news/n214196157.shtml |archivedate=2011-02-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

本次残奥会一共有创纪录的76个代表团赢得奖牌，另外70个代表团没有奖牌<ref name="peoplesdaily">{{Cite news |url=http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/90001/90779/90867/6501446.html |title=Day 12: China biggest winner at Paralympics |date=2008-09-17 |newspaper=Xinhua/People's Daily |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605191040/http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/90001/90779/90867/6501446.html |archivedate=2011-06-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。来自[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会克罗地亚代表团|克罗地亚]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://dalje.com/en-sports/photo--best-croatian-paralympic-athletes-of-2008/231520 |title=Best Croatian Paralympic Athletes Of 2008 |last=Horvat |first=Karmen |date=2009-02-06 |newspaper=Dalje.com |accessdate=2013-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113024432/http://dalje.com/en-sports/photo--best-croatian-paralympic-athletes-of-2008/231520 |archivedate=2012-11-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会蒙古代表团|蒙古]]<ref name="Mongolia">{{Cite news |url=http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/archery/n214601931.shtml |title=Dambadondog wins Mongolia's first ever Paralympic medal |date=2008-09-14 |newspaper=''Beijing 2008'' |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090422182118/http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/archery/n214601931.shtml |archivedate=2009-04-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会沙特阿拉伯代表团|沙特阿拉伯]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/athletics/n214591867.shtml |title=Osamah wins Saudi Arabia's first gold |date=2008-09-08 |newspaper=''Beijing 2008'' |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207035224/http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/sports/athletics/n214591867.shtml |archivedate=2009-02-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会新加坡代表团|新加坡]]<ref name="sing">{{Cite news |url=http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/special/features/n214606123.shtml |title=Yip's year: A sweet sixteen |date=2008-09-17 |newspaper=''Beijing 2008'' |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120416101250/http://en.paralympic.beijing2008.cn/news/special/features/n214606123.shtml |archivedate=2012-04-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会委内瑞拉代表团|委内瑞拉]]的残疾人运动员赢得了各自参加残奥会历史上的首枚金牌<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/paralympics/2008-09/15/content_7028462.htm |title=Venezuela sports minister hails Beijing Paralympics as "perfect" |date=2008-09-15 |newspaper=China Daily |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100711061522/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/paralympics/2008-09/15/content_7028462.htm |archivedate=2010-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。东道主[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会中国代表团|中国]]以总数211枚奖牌，其中89枚金牌高居榜首，[[2008年夏季残疾人奥林匹克运动会英国代表团|英国]]以102枚奖牌，其中42枚金牌位居第二<ref name="general information" /><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.abc.net.au/paralympics/2008/results/medaltally/ |title=2008 Medal Tally |newspaper=ABC |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081026061334/http://www.abc.net.au/paralympics/2008/results/medaltally/ |archivedate=2008-10-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。加拿大[[轮椅竞速|轮椅竞速]]运动员香岱儿·帕蒂可莱克（{{lang|en|Chantal Petitclerc}}）、分别来自南非和澳大利亚的S9级游泳运动员纳塔莉·杜托伊特（{{lang|en|Natalie du Toit}}）和马修·考德利（{{lang|en|Matthew Cowdrey}}）各赢得了5枚金牌<ref name=peoplesdaily/>，来自巴西的S5级游泳运动员丹尼尔·迪亚斯（{{lang|en|Daniel Dias}}）是赢得奖牌总数的第一人<ref name="laureus">{{Cite news |url=http://www.laureus.com/content/daniel-dias |title=Daniel Dias |newspaper=''Laureus'' |accessdate=2013-07-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028213612/http://www.laureus.com/content/daniel-dias |archivedate=2012-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，共计有9枚奖牌，其中4金4银1铜<ref name="general information" />。

